Justice League (2011-) Issue 45

▸ In the aftermath of the cataclysmic events of JUSTICE LEAGUE #44, members of the League have gained great power—the power of Gods!—but at a great price. And that price may be their destruction, unless Wonder Woman and MisterMiracle can help the League escape the curse of the New Gods and hold on to their humanity.
